        <item>
            <title>Hive 1.4.2</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <style type="text/css">
                    h2 { font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; }
                    ul { font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 10pt; }
                    li { margin: 5px 0px; }
                    </style>

                    <h2>What's changed:</h2>

                    <ul>
                    <li>added a one-time popup about the Hive 2.0 crowdfunding</li>
                    <li>added sending anonymous system stats to developers (if you agree)</li>
                    <li>fixed some problems with entering fiat currency amounts</li>
                    <li>fiat currency list is updated automatically based on what is supported by BitcoinAverage</li>
                    <li>added "Other Hive Products" link in the Hive menu</li>
                    <li>updated links in the About dialog - now linking to the new site (mac.hivewallet.com) and new Twitter profile (@hive_mac)</li>
                    <li>minor fixes and improvements</li>
                    </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
